														"target": null,
														"uri": null
													},
													"value": "Cyber security today needs a paradigm shift. Teams need to implement a comprehensive, value-based approach to security. And they need to hold partners and vendors accountable. Because being increasingly pessimistic about the effectiveness of cyber security solutions isn't a solution in and of itself. ",
